title: `Cat lover` Taylor Swift reunites with her furry friends
text:
*Washington, Oct. 5(ANI): Taylor Swift finally got a chance to reunite with her furry friends, whom she has been missing due to her 1989 tour.*
Washington, Oct. 5(ANI): Taylor Swift finally got a chance to reunite with her furry friends, whom she has been missing due to her 1989 tour. The 25-year-old singer who previously wrote on Instagram , "When you can't take your cats to Canada so you hug a cardboard version of them, But it's NOT THE SAME," met her cats on October 4, reports E! Online. Posting a picture with her cat, the 'Bad Blood' hit-maker posted, "Meredith is allergic to joy." (ANI) Â»
